/*
 *   Project F1 Racing Circuit
 *
 *  F1 Racing Circuit
 *
 *  Key bindings:
 *  p/P        Cycle through different Perspectives
 *  w/a/s/d    Move POV/Drive car (in POV mode)
 *  m/M        Cycle through different display modes
 *  q          Toggle axes
 *  arrows     Change view angle in perspective mode
 *  0          Reset view angle
 *  ESC        Exit
 *  [          Lower light
 *  ]          Higher light
 *  l,L        Toggle light
 *  F3         Toggle light distance
 *
 * use make command to get the binaries
 * ./final to view the project
 * In perspective mode, the camera is positioned behind the car, and you can drive the car using w/a/s/d keys.
 * Need to draw the grandstand and few types of stand modified to make it look more realistic.
 * The frame at the start line will have 4 types of components fixed (start line traffic lights, cameras, spotlight, sponsor banners).
 * Switching between different views based on camera position.
 * Simulate movement in other cars too.
 * Add lights.
 * Add textures to all objects.
 * Night mode with fog and rain effects.
 *
